globs: lib/**/*.dart
alwaysApply: false
---

# Dart conventions

- File names: `snake_case.dart`. Classes: `PascalCase`.
- Suffixes: `*_page.dart`, `*_bloc.dart`, `*_event.dart`, `*_state.dart`, `*_failure.dart`, `*_repository.dart`, `*_dto.dart`, `*_mapper.dart`, `*_service.dart`.
- Use `package:[[project_name]]/...` imports (`always_use_package_imports`).
- Specify types explicitly in `fold`, `catch`, `BlocBuilder`, and `switch` on Freezed states.
- Freezed + json_serializable + injectable: after editing annotated files run:
  `dart run build_runner build --delete-conflicting-outputs`
- Respect `analysis_options.yaml` in project root.
